Real Time clock commands (as per cmos-rtc data sheet):

	SECOND         0x00  //Second       (00..59) 
	MINUTE         0x02  //Minute       (00..59)
	HOUR           0x04  //Hour         (00..23) 
	DAY_IN_WEEK    0x06  //Day of week  (01..07)
	DAY            0x07  //Day          (01..31) 
	MONTH          0x08  //Month        (01..12) 
	YEAR           0x09  //Year         (00..99) 

Address mapping (IBM PC STANDARD) details :

ADDRESS_REG       0x70
DATA_REG          0x71
ADDRESS_REG_MASK  0xe0

